  "texts": [
    "This post-assessment process was classified into four categories:",
    "• Emotions: A category in which the feelings of the user during the experience were assessed.",
    "If biosensors were included in the experience, the data that were collected helped to understand the emotional relationship of the user with the application, e.g., anxiety, fear.",
    "• Features of the experience: To understand the opinion of the user towards the experience (e.g., cybersickness), its features are analyzed.",
    "This category includes general interviews or surveys on the experience and its development."
  ],
